## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f1504-102">사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> 작업과 <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> 를 대화형으로 중지는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> action with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to interactively stop a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f1504-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> 에 적용을 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> 활성 상태인 경우 (후를 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> 시작)입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1504-104">스토리 보드 트리거를 중지 합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> 이벤트를 하지 않고는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> 이벤트.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f1504-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 참조 하지 않는 한 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> 직접.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1504-106">아니라 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 를 참조 해야 합니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> 의 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 제어 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1504-107">참조 [방법: 이벤트 트리거는 Storyboard를 시작한 후 제어를 사용 하 여](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) 예입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="pause-resume-stop-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="f1504-108">일시 중지, 다시 시작, 중지 또는 그렇지 않은 경우 스토리 보드를 대화형으로 제어</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-108">Pause, Resume, Stop, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="f1504-109">있으려면 일시 중지, 다시 시작 또는 제어를 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> 대화형으로 설정 합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> 의 속성 해당 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 사용 하 여를 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> 개체 (와 같은 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>)에서 제어 참조는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-109">To be able to pause, resume, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1504-110">경우는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> 의 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 지정 되어 있지는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> 으로 시작한 후에 대화형으로 제어할 수 없습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1504-110">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1504-111">참조 [방법: 이벤트 트리거는 Storyboard를 시작한 후 제어를 사용 하 여](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphi